settings.description: Giant enemies among this plains stage.
Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
luigi needs to stop, this is getting tiring
watch out! while there may be some nice treasure at the end, you'll need to use some lavaproof beachballs to cross through this dangerous pipeline!
Venture through a switch-and-money-filled world of speedrunning, careful timing, precise jumps, and more! There's also an E-Coin up high in space, waiting to be found!

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5
A fun little holiday special. Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays!
